{
  "_meta": {
    "schema_version": 1,
    "description": "Hand-curated catalog of KM built-in action types. Each entry pairs a stable snake_case identifier with the KM MacroActionType (when known), human-readable description, search keywords, and parameter hints. Search and discovery read this; the builder reads km_action_templates.json keyed by MacroActionType. `builder_supported: true` means km_action_builder can emit XML for this type — either via a legacy hand-written emitter in action_builder_tools._build_action_xml (identifier matched first) or via a captured template in km_action_templates.json (MacroActionType matched second). The Phase 3 scrape will inflate this file to ~150 entries."
  },
  "actions": [
